),(868,1663,2,'Homepage','2022-04-14 09:49:59','2022-04-14 09:49:59','99962a50-386a-4933-8d44-64c811fbb629','<h3><strong>Welcome to Panda Engineering</strong></h3><br /><p>If you’re looking for expert welding, fabrication and CNC machining services across West Yorkshire, look no further than Panda Engineering. We’re a leading manufacturing company based in Bradford offering high-quality fabrication, sheet metalwork and precision CNC machining services for a wide range of applications. With a highly skilled team and dedication to the highest quality standards, Panda is able to deliver fast turnaround fabrications and CNC machined components to exact specifications for their customers in West Yorkshire and surrounding areas. </p>\n<p><strong>We Prioritise:</strong></p>\n<ul><li><p>LISTENING TO CUSTOMERS</p></li><li><p>FAST RESPONSE TIMES</p></li><li><p>RIGHT FIRST TIME</p></li><li>FLEXIBILITY &amp; ADAPTABILITY</li><li><p>BEING EASY TO DO BUSINESS WITH</p></li><li><p>HEALTH AND SAFETY IN THE WORKPLACE</p></li><li><p>NO QUIBBLE GUARANTEE*</p></li></ul><p><em>*We guarantee that in the event of any query or rejection, we will always prioritise your delivery schedule above all else.</em></p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(870,1673,2,'Fabrication & Sheet Metal Services','2022-04-14 09:51:35','2022-04-14 09:51:35','1ce7b20a-7e91-4c33-bba6-9b9b3f917fff',NULL,NULL,'<p>Panda Engineering has many years of experience in fabrication services, steel fabrication and sheet metalwork. From your initial fabrication design concept right through to delivery of the finished product, we have the skills and experience to successfully complete the job and deliver within your timescale and budget. Seeking bespoke fabrications and sheet metalwork services? Contact Panda Engineering today.</p>',NULL,NULL,'{\"bundleVersion\":\"1.0.22\",\"sourceBundleType\":\"field\",\"sourceId\":null,\"sourceName\":null,\"sourceHandle\":null,\"sourceType\":\"field\",\"typeId\":null,\"sourceTemplate\":\"\",\"source