ial conceptualisation all the way to the finished product.</p>\n<p>What’s more, we are well versed at working to a range of budgets and timeframes. So, if you’re seeking high-quality metal fabrication services, get in touch with our team today. We’re always happy to help.</p>\n<h2>Services</h2>\n<p>We offer a wide range of fabrication services to suit our clients’ varied requirements. From staircases and walkways to guarding platforms and bespoke sheet metalwork, we have experience completing a wide range of projects. </p>',NULL,NULL,'{\"bundleVersion\":\"1.0.22\",\"sourceBundleType\":\"field\",\"sourceId\":null,\"sourceName\":null,\"sourceHandle\":null,\"sourceType\":\"field\",\"typeId\":null,\"sourceTemplate\":\"\",\"sourceSiteId\":null,\"sourceAltSiteSettings\":[],\"sourceDateUpdated\":\"2022-04-14T10:51:21+01:00\",\"metaGlobalVars\":{\"language\":null,\"mainEntityOfPage\":\"\",\"seoTitle\":\"Panda Engineering | Fabrication & Metalwork Services\",\"siteNamePosition\":\"\",\"seoDescription\":\"At Panda Engineering, we offer sheet metalwork, bespoke fabrication and engineering services across West Yorkshire and Bradford. Contact our team today.\",\"seoKeywords\":\"\",\"seoImage\":\"\",\"seoImageWidth\":\"\",\"seoImageHeight\":\"\",\"seoImageDescription\":\"\",\"canonicalUrl\":\"\",\"robots\":\"\",\"ogType\":\"\",\"ogTitle\":\"\",\"ogSiteNamePosition\":\"\",\"ogDescription\":\"\",\"ogImage\":\"\",\"ogImageWidth\":\"\",\"ogImageHeight\":\"\",\"ogImageDescription\":\"\",\"twitterCard\":\"\",\"twitterCreator\":\"\",\"twitterTitle\":\"\",\"twitterSiteNamePosition\":\"\",\"twitterDescription\":\"\",\"twitterImage\":\"\",\"twitterImageWidth\":\"\",\"twitterImageHeight\":\"\",\"twitterImageDescription\":\"\",\"inherited\":{\"seoKeywords\":true,\"seoImage\":true},\"overrides\":{\"seoTitle\":true,\"seoDescription\":true}},\"metaSiteVars\":{\"siteName\":\"Panda Engineering\",\"identity\":null,\"creator\":null,\"twitterHandle\":\"\",\"facebookProfileId\":\"\",\"facebookAppId\"