\"seoImageDescriptionField\":\"\",\"twitterCreatorSource\":\"\",\"twitterCreatorField\":\"\",\"twitterTitleSource\":\"\",\"twitterTitleField\":\"\",\"twitterSiteNamePositionSource\":\"\",\"twitterDescriptionSource\":\"\",\"twitterDescriptionField\":\"\",\"twitterImageIds\":[],\"twitterImageSource\":\"\",\"twitterImageField\":\"\",\"twitterImageTransform\":true,\"twitterImageTransformMode\":\"crop\",\"twitterImageDescriptionSource\":\"\",\"twitterImageDescriptionField\":\"\",\"ogTitleSource\":\"\",\"ogTitleField\":\"\",\"ogSiteNamePositionSource\":\"\",\"ogDescriptionSource\":\"\",\"ogDescriptionField\":\"\",\"ogImageIds\":[],\"ogImageSource\":\"\",\"ogImageField\":\"\",\"ogImageTransform\":true,\"ogImageTransformMode\":\"crop\",\"ogImageDescriptionSource\":\"\",\"ogImageDescriptionField\":\"\"}}'),(1004,2152,2,'Homepage','2025-10-06 08:17:38','2025-10-06 08:17:38','9e2053f1-0ced-4536-8e0c-5e0d84bc9d0e','<h3><strong>Welcome to Panda Engineering</strong></h3>\n\n<p><br /></p>\n<p>At Panda Engineering, we are experts in our field. If you’re looking for high-quality fabrication, sheet metal work, CNC machining and professional welding services across West Yorkshire, then look no further than Panda Engineering. We have a highly skilled team based in Bradford who are committed to delivering only the highest quality services in the industry. </p>\n<p>Suitable to a wide range of both commercial and domestic industries, Panda Engineering is assured to have the engineering solution for you.</p>\n<p>As the leading manufacturing company in Bradford, we are able to deliver fast turnaround fabrication and CNC machined components to exact specifications for our customers in West Yorkshire and surrounding areas.</p>\n\n<p><strong>We prioritise:</strong></p>\n<ul><li>LISTENING TO CUSTOMERS</li><li>FAST RESPONSE TIMES</li><li>BEING RIGHT FIRST TIME</li><li>FLEXIBILITY AND ADAPTABILITY</li><li>BEING EASY TO WORK WITH</li><li>HEALTH AND SAFETY</li><li>NO QUIBBLE GUARANTEE</li></ul><p>*We guarantee that in the event of any query or rejection, we will always prioritise your delivery schedule above all else.</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(1006,2156,2,'Homepage','2025-10-06 08:21:30','2025-10-06 08:21:30','81b4acbb-b019-4eba-b3c0-3e2fd37ad6a5','<h3><strong>Welcome to Panda Engineering</strong></h3>\n<p>At <strong>Panda Engineering</strong>, we are experts in precision engineering and power transmission solutions. From <strong>high-quality fabrication and sheet metal work</strong> to <strong>CNC machining, welding, and transmission component manufacture</strong>, our Bradford-based team delivers exceptional workmanship across <strong>West Yorkshire and the UK</strong>.</p>\n<p>We specialise in producing <strong>custom power transmission parts</strong>, including <strong>shafts, couplings, gears, and bearing housings</strong>, alongside our full range of CNC-machined and fabricated components. With advanced in-house equipment and a skilled engineering team, we ensure every project meets the highest standards of accuracy, strength, and finish.</p>\n<p>Serving a wide range of <strong>commercial, industrial, and maintenance sectors</strong>, <strong>Panda Engineering</strong> provides complete engineering solutions — from one-off prototypes to high-volume production. As one of <strong>Bradford’s leading precision engineering companies</strong>, we’re proud to offer <strong>fast turnaround times, dependable quality, and exceptional customer service</strong><br /><br /></p>\n\n<p>*We guarantee that in the event of any query or rejection, we will always prioritise your delivery schedule above all else.</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(1008,2160,2,'Homepage','2025-10-06 08:22:11','2025-10-06 08:22:11','07ce536d-1630-42a0-a81e-387508960344','<h3>At <strong>Panda Engineering</strong>, we are experts in precision engineering and power transmission solutions. From <strong>high-quality fabrication and sheet metal work</strong> to <strong>CNC machining, welding, an