elivery schedule above all else.</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(1014,2172,2,'Homepage','2025-10-06 08:29:52','2025-10-06 08:29:52','eea49d19-276f-477a-9bed-df4fc504dd39','<p>At <strong>Panda Engineering</strong>, we are experts in <strong>precision engineering and power transmission solutions</strong>. From <strong>high-quality fabrication and sheet metal work</strong> to <strong>CNC machining, welding, and transmission component supply</strong>, our Bradford-based team delivers exceptional workmanship across <strong>West Yorkshire and the UK</strong>.</p>\n<p>We <strong>supply both manufactured and proprietary power transmission components</strong>, including <strong>shafts, couplings, gears, and bearing housings</strong>, alongside our full range of CNC-machined and fabricated parts. With advanced in-house capabilities and trusted supply partnerships, we ensure every component meets the highest standards of <strong>quality, fit, and performance</strong>.</p>\n<p>Serving a wide range of <strong>commercial, industrial, and maintenance sectors</strong>, <strong>Panda Engineering</strong> provides complete engineering solutions — from <strong>one-off prototypes</strong> to <strong>high-volume production</strong>. As one of <strong>Bradford’s leading precision engineering companies</strong>, we’re committed to delivering <strong>fast turnaround times, dependable quality, and exceptional customer service</strong>.</p>\n<p>&#x1f449; <strong>Get in touch today</strong> to discuss your project or request a free quotation — and discover how Panda Engineering can keep your business moving with precision, reliability, and expertise.</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(1016,2176,2,'Homepage','2025-10-06 08:38:23','2025-10-06 08:38:23','a5c63bcd-9537-44d4-8a94-8bb7db55c579','<p>At <strong>Panda Engineering</strong>, we are specialists in <strong>precision engineering and power transmission solutions</strong>. From <strong>high-quality fabrication and sheet metal work</strong> to <strong>welding, CNC machining</strong>, and <strong>transmission component supply</strong>, our Bradford-based team delivers exceptional workmanship across <strong>West Yorkshire and the UK</strong>.</p>\n<p>We <strong>supply both manufactured and proprietary power transmission components</strong>, including <strong>shafts, couplings, gears, and bearing housings</strong>, alongside our comprehensive <strong>CNC machining and fabrication services</strong>. With advanced in-house capabilities and trusted supply partnerships, we ensure every component meets the highest standards of <strong>quality, accuracy, and performance</strong>.</p>\n<p>Serving a wide range of <strong>commercial, industrial, and maintenance sectors</strong>, <strong>Panda Engineering</strong> provides complete engineering solutions — from <strong>one-off prototypes</strong> to <strong>high-volume production</strong>. As one of <strong>Bradford’s leading precision engineering companies</strong>, we’re dedicated to delivering <strong>fast turnaround times, dependable quality, and exceptional customer service</strong>.</p>\n<p>&#x1f449; <strong>Contact us today</strong> at <strong><a>info@panda-engineering.co.uk</a></strong> or call <strong>01274 744 887</strong> to discuss your project or request a free quotation — and discover how <strong>Panda Engineering</strong> can keep your business moving with <strong>precision, reliability, and expertise.</strong></p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(1018,2186,2,'Precision CNC Machining','2025-10-06 08:40:47','2025-10-06 08:40:47','ebcdd5c6-651f-4314-9162-48176fdbe2fe',NULL,NULL,'<p>At Panda Engineering, we are renowned for our high-quality CNC machining services. Supplying components for CNC milling machines, CNC turning machines and CNC bar feeding machines, our machined components are built to serve a wide range of industries.</p>',NULL,NULL,'{\"bundleVersion\":\"1.0.22\",\"sourceBundleType\":\"field\",\"sourceId\":null,\"sourceName\":null,\"sourceHandle\":nul