ing and fabrication services</strong>. With advanced in-house capabilities and trusted supply partnerships, we ensure every component meets the highest standards of <strong>quality, accuracy, and performance</strong>.</p>\n<p>Serving a wide range of <strong>commercial, industrial, and maintenance sectors</strong>, <strong>Panda Engineering</strong> provides complete engineering solutions — from <strong>one-off prototypes</strong> to <strong>high-volume production</strong>. As one of <strong>Bradford’s leading precision engineering companies</strong>, we’re dedicated to delivering <strong>fast turnaround times, dependable quality, and exceptional customer service</strong>.</p>\n<p>&#x1f449; <strong>Contact us today</strong> at <strong><a>info@panda-engineering.co.uk</a></strong> or call <strong>01274 744 887</strong> to discuss your project or request a free quotation — and discover how <strong>Panda Engineering</strong> can keep your business moving with <strong>precision, reliability, and expertise.</strong></p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(1086,2922,2,'HSE POLICY POL003 issue 4','2025-10-06 10:08:48','2025-10-06 10:08:48','3b8a96d9-eb85-4313-b026-f13edac162c5',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(1088,2932,2,'Power Transmission & Bearing Solutions','2025-10-06 11:43:56','2025-10-06 11:43:56','689fba4d-978d-4405-9355-dd700850db55',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'{\"bundleVersion\":\"1.0.22\",\"sourceBundleType\":\"field\",\"sourceId\":null,\"sourceName\":null,\"sourceHandle\":null,\"sourceType\":\"field\",\"typeId\":null,\"sourceTemplate\":\"\",\"sourceSiteId\":null,\"sourceAltSiteSettings\":[],\"sourceDateUpdated\":\"2022-07-05T16:13:45+01:00\",\"metaGlobalVars\":{\"language\":null,\"mainEntityOfPage\":\"\",\"seoTitle\":\"Panda Engineering | Precision CNC Machining & Milling\",\"siteNamePosition\":\"\",\"seoDescription\":\"Seeking CNC milling and machining services in West Yorkshire? At Panda Engineering, we provide expert CNC precision machining services. Contact us today. \