k and fabrication to installation and maintenance services.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>“We’re thrilled to receive SafeContractor approval,” said Kieran Doyle, Managing Director at Panda Engineering. “It’s a reflection of our ongoing commitment to maintaining the highest standards of safety and professionalism for our employees, clients, and partners. This accreditation gives our customers added confidence that every project we undertake is managed safely, responsibly, and in full compliance with current legislation.”</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Achieving this certification required a comprehensive review of Panda Engineering’s health and safety policies, procedures, and records. By passing this assessment, Panda Engineering joins a respected network of SafeContractor-approved companies dedicated to operating safely and responsibly.</p>\n<p>At Panda Engineering, we believe that strong safety practices are the foundation of quality workmanship. The SafeContractor accreditation reinforces our reputation as a trusted partner in the engineering and fabrication industry — delivering reliable, high-quality solutions while keeping safety at the forefront of everything we do.</p>\n<p>For more information about Panda Engineering and our services, visit <a><strong>www.panda-engineering.co.uk</strong></a></p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(1090,2942,2,'Panda Engineering Achieves SafeContractor Accreditation for Excellence in Health and Safety','2025-10-06 12:31:07','2025-10-06 12:31:07','3ac8df84-338e-4f4f-abb2-474c77288104','<h3>Panda Engineering is proud to announce that we have been awarded the <strong>SafeContractor accreditation</strong>, a leading third-party certification that recognises companies committed to achieving excellence in health and safety standards in the workplace.</h3>\n<p>The <strong>SafeContractor scheme</strong>, operated by Alcumus, is one of the UK’s most respected health and safety assessment schemes. The accreditation demonstrates that Panda Engineering has met the rigorous standards required to ensure safe working practices across all our operations — from site work and fabrication to installation and maintenance services.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>“We’re thrilled to receive SafeContractor approval,” said Kieran Doyle, Managing Director at Panda Engineering. “It’s a reflection of our ongoing commitment to maintaining the highest standards of safety and professionalism for our employees, clients, and partners. This accreditation gives our customers added confidence that every project we undertake is managed safely, responsibly, and in full compliance with current legislation.”</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Achieving this certification required a comprehensive review of Panda Engineering’s health and safety policies, procedures, and records. By passing this assessment, Panda Engineering joins a respected network of SafeContractor-approved companies dedicated to operating safely and responsibly.</p>\n<p>At Panda Engineering, we believe that strong safety practices are the foundation of quality workmanship. The SafeContractor accreditation reinforces our reputation as a trusted partner in the engineering and fabrication industry — delivering reliable, high-quality solutions while keeping safety at the forefront of everything we do.</p>\n<p>For more information about Panda Engineering and our services, visit <a><strong>www.pandaengineering.co.uk</strong></a>.</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(1092,2944,2,'Panda Engineering Achieves SafeContractor Accreditation for Excellence in Health and Safety','2025-10-06 12:34:12','2025-10-06 12:34:12','e68acb98-c513-4517-a8b9-3dc32dbc8177','<h3>Panda Engineering is proud to announce that we have been awarded the <strong>SafeContractor accreditation</strong>, a leading third-party certification that recognises companies committed to achieving excellence in health and safety standards in the workplace.</h3>\n<p>The <strong>SafeContractor scheme</strong>, operated by Alcumus, is one of the UK’s most respected health and safety assessment schemes. The accreditation demonstrates that Panda Engineering has met the rigorous standards required to ensure safe working practices across all our operations — from site work and fabrication to installation and maintenance services.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>“We’re thrilled to receive SafeContractor approval,” said Kieran Doyle, Managing Director at Panda Engineering. “It’s a reflection of our ongoing commitment to maintaining the highest standards of safety and professionalism for our employees, clients, and partners. This accreditation gives our customers added confidence that every project we undertake is managed safely, responsibly, and in full compliance with current legislation.”</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Achieving this certification required a comprehensive review of Panda Engineering’s health and safety policies, procedures, and records. By passing this assessment, Panda Engineering joins a respected network of SafeContractor-approved companies dedicated to operating safely and responsibly.</p>\n<p>At Panda Engineering, we believe that strong safety practices are the foundation of quality workmanship. The SafeContractor accreditation reinforces our reputation as a trusted partner in the engineering and fabrication industry — delivering reliable, high-quality solutions while keeping safety at the forefront of everything we do.</p>\n<p>For more information about Panda Engineering and our services, visit <a><strong>www.panda-engineering.co.uk</strong></a></p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(1095,2954,2,'Precision CNC Machining Services','2025-10-08 12:54:44','2025-10-08 12:54:44','ca128d53-8a1f-42b9-910b-3bbdeaf1069e',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'{\"bundleVersion\":\"1.0.22\",\"sourceBundleType\":\"field\",\"sourceId\":null,\"sourceName\":null,\"sourceHandle\":null,\"sourceType\":\"field\",\"typeId\":null,\"sourceTemplate\":\"\",\"sourceSiteId\":null,\"sourceAltSiteSettings\":[],\"sourceDateUpdated\":\"2022-07-05T16:13:45+01:00\",\"meta