strong>shafts, couplings, gears, and bearing housings</strong>, alongside our comprehensive <strong>CNC machining and fabrication services</strong>. With advanced in-house capabilities and trusted supply partnerships, we ensure every component meets the highest standards of <strong>quality, accuracy, and performance</strong>.</p>\n<p>Serving a wide range of <strong>commercial, industrial, and maintenance sectors</strong>, <strong>Panda Engineering</strong> provides complete engineering solutions — from <strong>one-off prototypes</strong> to <strong>high-volume production</strong>. As one of <strong>Bradford’s leading precision engineering companies</strong>, we’re dedicated to delivering <strong>fast turnaround times, dependable quality, and exceptional customer service</strong>.</p>\n<p>&#x1f449; <strong>Contact us today</strong> at <strong><a>info@panda-engineering.co.uk</a></strong> or call <strong>01274 744 887</strong> to discuss your project or request a free quotation — and discover how <strong>Panda Engineering</strong> can keep your business moving with <strong>precision, reliability, and expertise.</strong></p>',':light_bulb:Click on the images to find out more!',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(1139,3294,2,'Homepage','2025-10-08 15:54:59','2025-10-08 15:54:59','fe8263b7-b648-4485-ada9-a60d018a2923','<p>At <strong>Panda Engineering</strong>, we are specialists in <strong>precision engineering and power transmission solutions</strong>. From <strong>high-quality fabrication and sheet metal work</strong> to <strong>welding, CNC machining</strong>, and <strong>transmission component supply</strong>, our Bradford-based team delivers exceptional workmanship across <strong>West Yorkshire and the UK</strong>.</p>\n<p>We <strong>supply both manufactured and proprietary power transmission components</strong>, including <strong>shafts, couplings, gears, and bearing housings</strong>, alongside our comprehensive <strong>CNC machining and fabrication services</strong>. With advan