icator.</p>\n<p>Get in touch for all your alloy wheel repair / straightening requirements on 01274 744887</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(135,933,2,'2020-06-10 13:42:46','2020-06-10 13:42:46','5b0c2ad0-581b-4b10-8883-fb1eb229c4c7',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(136,945,2,'2020-06-10 13:42:47','2020-06-10 13:42:47','bffd9b47-ea87-469c-a5bc-cfb2672b3ae6','<h1>Transmission Products</h1>\n<p>As a full service engineering company we continually carry a comprehensive stock of items. These items are available for purchase, please call us to discuss your requirement.</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(137,964,2,'2020-06-10 13:46:43','2020-06-10 13:46:43','2c2b3e47-ab99-4f69-9c67-e412249676e4',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(138,976,2,'2020-06-10 13:46:43','2020-06-10 13:46:43','979dbca8-c8f0-4368-9c2d-6d3bdfb8cfb3','<h1>Transmission Products</h1>\n<p>As a full service engineering company we continually carry a comprehensive stock of items. These items are available for purchase, please call us to discuss your requirement.</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(139,1197,2,'2020-07-14 13:52:02','2020-07-14 13:52:02','f3b49136-4407-4f7d-be5d-440ecd3a2dd7',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Service List'),(140,1202,2,'2020-07-14 13:52:02','2020-07-14 13:52:02','17315d67-0cdd-4702-9062-e990aceabdc7',NULL,'[{\"col1\":\"XYZ 4 axis Mini Mill multi tool machining centre with 500 x 500 x 450mm travelling capacity\"},{\"col1\":\"XYZ 2 axis KRV 3000 milling machine X 2 with 900 x 450 x 350mm travelling capacity\"},{\"col1\":\"XYZ 3 axis SMX 5000 milling machine with 1450 x 650 x 500mm travelling capacity\"},{\"col1\":\"XYZ 3 axis DPM milling machine with 850 x 500 x 500mm travelling capacity\"},{\"col1\":\"XYZ 250T CNC lathe with bar feed 75mm diameter bar feed capacity\"},{\"col1\":\"Hyundai Hit 20m CNC lathe with live tooling and bar feed 65mm diameter bar feed capacity\"},{\"col1\":\"Hyundai Hit 30f CNC lathe with bar feed 90mm diameter capacity\"},{\"col1\":\"Toss “long bed” lathe with 4000mm capacity between centres\"},{\"col1\