r cracks stress fractures or kerb damage whilst maintaining the wheel strength and integrity the first step of the repair process is to grind both sides of the crack to remove any contamination therefore giving a clean weld step 2 is to tig weld inside and outside of the alloy wheel once the weld is complete it is as strong as a new wheel finally we will dress the weld back on the inside of the wheel which allows the tyre to re seal correctly we also offer alloy wheel straightening we mount the wheel onto our straightening machine and heat the affected area using a small propane torch this stops the wheel cracking hydraulic cylinders are used to press the wheel back into shape the wheel is then spun and checked for straightness using a dial test indicator get in touch for all your alloy wheel repair straightening requirements on 01274 744887 '),(1315,'filename',0,2,' vessel manufacture jpg '),(462,'kind',0,2,' image '),(462,'slug',0,2,''),(462,'title',0,2,' s lxwlds ii ouc wr crearsc zkc gq ds3v72 gy pnpo y ov m '),(462,'extension',0,2,' jpg '),(462,'filename',0,2,' slxwldsii oucwrcrearsczkcgqds3v72gypnpoyovm jpg '),(462,'filename',0,1,' slxwldsii oucwrcrearsczkcgqds3v72gypnpoyovm jpg '),(462,'extension',0,1,' jpg '),(462,'kind',0,1,' image '),(462,'slug',0,1,''),(462,'title',0,1,' s lxwlds ii ouc wr crearsc zkc gq ds3v72 gy pnpo y ov m '),(463,'kind',0,2,' image '),(463,'slug',0,2,''),(463,'title',0,2,' 7yp0dl xa8qsd g4 e6 kfr sb v3s r iim u2h u3 v0x q uq cw '),(463,'extension',0,2,' jpg '),(463,'filename',0,2,' 7yp0dlxa8qsdg4e6kfrsbv3sriimu2hu3v0xq uq cw jpg '),(463,'filename',0,1,' 7yp0dlxa8qsdg4e6kfrsbv3sriimu2hu3v0xq uq cw jpg '),(463,'extension',0,1,' jpg '),(463,'kind',0,1,' image '),(463,'slug',0,1,''),(463,'title',0,1,' 7yp0dl xa8qsd g4 e6 kfr sb v3s r iim u2h u3 v0x q uq cw '),(464,'kind',0,2,' image '),(464,'slug',0,2,''),(464,'title',0,2,' bn rf pq xeo6gxbzvr l ei uep 9 ew zp47c yp1hy srk7s '),(464,'extension',0,2,' jpg '),(464,'filename',0,2,' bnrfpqxeo