426,2,'2020-05-12 14:16:37','2020-05-12 14:16:37','2dd146dc-5bb8-4b23-a666-e5dabd920485','Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Quisque mollis auctor enim suscipit euismod. Curabitur sit amet nisl eget ligula porta iaculis.'),(41,433,2,'2020-05-12 14:19:43','2025-10-06 11:43:56','3182179c-6a74-456c-8967-99270ca429ac','<p>At <strong>Panda Engineering</strong>, we supply and manufacture a comprehensive range of <strong>high-performance power transmission components and bearing solutions</strong>. From precision-machined shafts and couplings to custom bearing housings and gear assemblies, parts can be produced to exacting standards in our fully equipped CNC facility. Whether you need bespoke one-off components, small batch production, or ongoing supply of critical spares, our in-house expertise ensures reliability, durability, and performance across every application.</p>\n<p>If you’re looking for a trusted local partner for <strong>bearings and power transmission products</strong>, backed by precision engineering and responsive service, <strong>Panda Engineering</strong> delivers quality you can depend on.</p>\n<p> </p>'),(42,435,2,'2020-05-12 14:19:43','2020-05-12 14:19:43','74af9813-7742-4a76-84ee-81cd21edc9ef',NULL),(46,441,2,'2020-05-12 14:20:02','2025-10-06 09:33:29','45095d9e-b2c6-4e0c-8e49-99ecb4a967ef','<p>At <strong>Panda Engineering</strong>, we take pride in delivering <strong>high-quality bespoke fabrication and sheet metalwork services</strong>. With years of experience and a fully equipped workshop in <strong>Bradford, West Yorkshire</strong>, our skilled fabricators have the expertise to take your project from <strong>customer-supplied drawings or specifications</strong> through to <strong>accurate, reliable manufacture and installation</strong>.</p>\n<p>We work flexibly to meet your <strong>budget, schedule, and technical requirements</strong>, ensuring every job is completed safely, efficiently, and to the highest standards. Whether it’s a one-off item or part of a larger production run, you can rely on <strong>Panda Engineering</strong> for consistent quality and exceptional attention to detail.</p>'),(47,443,2,'2020-05-12 14:20:02','2020-05-12 14:20:02','fbbbad9c-6917-4885-ab8d-d75db2607c75',NULL),(52,450,2,'2020-05-12 14:20:15','2025-10-06 09:49:54','9a001982-d156-4e56-bbd6-b7603707dc96','<p>At <strong>Panda Engineering</strong>, we are proud to provide a comprehensive range of <strong>supporting engineering services</strong> that complement our core machining, fabrication, and power transmission work. With trusted partners and years of experience, we ensure every process is completed to the same high standard our customers expect — delivering <strong>quality, durability, and a flawless finish every time</strong>.</p>\n<p>Our extended capabilities allow us to manage complete projects efficiently, saving our clients time and simplifying their supply chain.</p>'),(53,452,2,'2020-05-12 14:20:15','2020-05-12 14:20:15','8efabbf7-628b-46b2-b826-3c2984295799',NULL),(54,461,2,'2020-05-12 14:38:37','2020-05-12 14:38:37','5927cf39-12d2-46d0-be37-0a741ed8abb0','Over the years we have built a reputation for our high quality CNC machining services, manufacturing a wide range of machined components for many different industries and applications.'),(55,470,2,'2020-05-12 14:47:49','2020-05-12 14:47:49','f82ceeb9-1a8f-4e5c-887e-6f19205d6b33','We offer fabrication and sheet metalwork solutions across a wide range of applications that incorporate domestic, commercial and industrial applications.'),(56,472,2,'2020-05-12 15:24:14','2020-05-12 15:24:14','9195f3e6-4b20-45d2-a229-fa8c2ac05fc8','Over the years we have built a reputation for our high quality CNC machining services, manufacturing a wide range of machined components for many different industries and applications.'),(57,474,2,'2020-05-12 15:25:50','2020-05-12 15:25:50','7838e325-7129-49db-a624-8ec481643704','We offer fabrication and sheet metalwork sol