:15:29','71411341-de61-4812-be77-8f356ce472d7','\n<p>We supply fabrication and sheet metal work solutions to a range of industries, both commercial and domestic, making us experts in our field. </p>\n'),(247,1800,2,'2022-08-05 13:37:45','2022-08-05 13:37:45','05b25bae-f91b-410f-90d8-08718a3de369','<p>We supply fabrication and sheet metal work solutions to a range of industries, both commercial and domestic, making us experts in our field. </p>'),(249,1823,2,'2022-08-05 13:39:27','2022-08-05 13:39:27','b587ab05-5e31-4341-a4ed-79354175a5f3','<p>We also offer a range of engineering support services including Coatings, Platings, Blasting, Anodising and Eroding.</p>'),(251,1894,2,'2024-01-29 16:00:38','2024-01-29 16:00:38','006cb6fa-97e0-453a-9cc4-78d3ef030cf2','<p>We also offer a range of engineering support services including Coatings, Platings, Blasting, Anodising and Eroding.</p>'),(254,1920,2,'2025-10-06 07:29:25','2025-10-06 09:15:36','9dc8086c-66de-438d-ad09-d57ffa5c70f2','<p>At <strong>Panda Engineering</strong>, we deliver a comprehensive range of <strong>in-house CNC milling and machining services</strong>, trusted by customers across <strong>Bradford, West Yorkshire, and the UK</strong>. From <strong>one-off prototypes</strong> to <strong>high-volume batch production</strong>, our skilled engineers produce precision-machined parts in a wide variety of materials — all to exact specifications and uncompromising standards.</p>\n<p>With advanced CNC equipment, experienced machinists, and a commitment to quality, we provide components that meet the most demanding industrial requirements. In addition to our in-house capabilities, we also offer <strong>outsourced wire erosion services</strong> through trusted partners, ensuring a complete machining solution from start to finish.</p>\n\n<p> </p>'),(255,1928,2,'2025-10-06 07:29:25','2025-10-06 07:29:25','cf89f31a-615a-432f-81b4-90e2e0152f18','<p>At Panda Engineering we offer a wide range of high quality ‘in-house’ subcontract CNC milling and machining services. From one-offs to high volume batch work, we provide only the highest quality precision machined parts and CNC components in a huge variety of materials. </p>\n<p>If you are looking for the best CNC milling and wire eroding services in the industry, look no further than Panda Engineering. </p>'),(257,1944,2,'2025-10-06 07:32:08','2025-10-06 07:32:08','49008493-5e43-4226-8460-9dcdfc620978','<p>At <strong>Panda Engineering</strong>, we supply and manufacture a comprehensive range of <strong>high-performance power transmission components and bearing solutions</strong>. From precision-machined shafts and couplings to custom bearing housings and gear assemblies, every part is produced to exacting standards in our fully equipped CNC facility. Whether you need bespoke one-off components, small batch production, or ongoing supply of critical spares, our in-house expertise ensures reliability, durability, and performance across every application.</p>\n<p>If you’re looking for a trusted local partner for <strong>bearings and power transmission products</strong>, backed by precision engineering and responsive service, <strong>Panda Engineering</strong> delivers quality you can depend on.</p>\n<p> </p>'),(259,1960,2,'2025-10-06 07:39:33','2025-10-06 07:39:33','46400a95-f034-4550-a622-20bd70653af0','<p>At <strong>Panda Engineering</strong>, we supply and manufacture a comprehensive range of <strong>high-performance power transmission components and bearing solutions</strong>. From precision-machined shafts and couplings to custom bearing housings and gear assemblies, every part is produced to exacting standards in our fully equipped CNC facility. Whether you need bespoke one-off components, small batch production, or ongoing supply of critical spares, our in-house expertise ensures reliability, durability, and performance across every application.</p>\n<p>If you’re looking for a trusted local partner for <strong>bearings and power trans